France 10.3%
Netherlands 8.1%
Germany 6.5%
Britain 5.8%</p>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Interesting fact to start  2015: 54% Labour PPCs have spent most of their working lives in the Westminster village - for Conservatives 17%!</p>
</div>

      <div class="modal-body">

  <form class="t1-form">

    <div class="embed-destination-wrapper">
      <div class="embed-overlay embed-overlay-spinner"><div class="embed-overlay-content"></div></div>

        <div class="embed-include-parent-tweet">
